is what I was trying to explain.

10:58.658 --> 10:59.950
They changed her.

11:00.034 --> 11:02.745
They've made me realize
that I can't be with an asshole

11:02.828 --> 11:05.831
-that uses my face as a punching bag.
-[father] Enough!

11:06.749 --> 11:07.583
Joaquin...

11:08.167 --> 11:09.418
get her bag.

11:19.178 --> 11:20.012
Huh...

11:36.278 --> 11:39.573
Want to go again... faggot?

11:46.705 --> 11:49.166
Only if you want your ass kicked
by a faggot.

11:49.250 --> 11:50.334
Again.

11:52.878 --> 11:54.004
Thank you.

11:54.088 --> 11:55.339
Stop it.

11:55.423 --> 11:56.966
I'm not going anywhere with you.

11:57.049 --> 11:58.801
Don't be a child, Daniela.

11:58.884 --> 12:00.386
Don't treat me like one.

12:00.469 --> 12:03.347
Everything I built in this world,
I built for you.

12:03.431 --> 12:05.099
But if you force me,

12:05.182 --> 12:07.226
I will cut you out of that world

12:07.309 --> 12:08.727
and I'll never look back.

12:08.811 --> 12:12.690
I know this is hard for all three of you
to understand,

12:12.773 --> 12:15.109
but I have a relationship
with these two men

12:15.192 --> 12:19.989
that isn't based on threats,
or control, or money.

12:20.072 --> 12:24.243
You're not allowed to be sanctimonious
when you're living off a trust fund.

12:26.370 --> 12:27.872
Keep your money.

12:28.456 --> 12:29.457
She doesn't need it.

12:31.542 --> 12:33.085
Daniela, please...

12:33.669 --> 12:35.671
come home with us.

12:39.091 --> 12:40.384
Sorry, Mom.

12:43.387 --> 12:44.638
I am home.

13:14.668 --> 13:16.795
["I Second That Emotion" playing]

13:16.879 --> 13:18.297
I'm home.

13:18.380 --> 13:20.216
Hey! Whoo-hoo!

13:21.383 --> 13:24.386
♪ Maybe you'll wanna give me
Kisses sweet ♪

13:24.470 --> 13:26.388
-Hi.
-One sec.

13:26.472 --> 13:28.265
♪ But only for one night with no repeat ♪

13:28.349 --> 13:29.517
-Is it Will again?
-Yeah.

13:30.935 --> 13:35.147
♪ And maybe you'll go away
And never call ♪

13:35.231 --> 13:37.191
Listen, I just want to know
what the plan is

13:37.274 --> 13:39.652
in case the ID doesn't work out.

13:39.735 --> 13:43.072
I'm telling you,
it's the best one I've ever done.

13:44.532 --> 13:47.952
And by the way,
how do you know so much about fake IDs?

13:48.786 --> 13:50.746
Every trans person needs a new ID.

13:50.829 --> 13:53.707
And when the government makes them
too hard to get, I make it easy.

13:54.375 --> 13:55.459
She's not through yet.

13:57.419 --> 13:58.504
It'll be fine.

13:59.672 --> 14:05.636
♪ So, if you feel like giving me
A lifetime of devotion ♪

14:06.220 --> 14:09.390
♪ I second that emotion ♪

14:10.391 --> 14:14.019
♪ Oh, little girl, I second that emotion ♪

14:20.025 --> 14:21.610
I know you feel we can trust Hoy,

14:21.694 --> 14:25.030
but if I were BPO,
I would be waiting for you here.

14:25.114 --> 14:27.825
If they know I'm here,
I don't think it will be because of Hoy.

14:30.744 --> 14:31.871
