14:32.663 --> 14:33.831
Excuse me.

14:34.415 --> 14:35.791
Diego!

14:39.420 --> 14:41.213
God, you're a sight for sore eyes.

14:41.297 --> 14:42.590
So...

14:43.632 --> 14:45.134
