14:50.973 --> 14:53.100
Both Will and I are so grateful.

14:54.977 --> 14:58.397
He said he was gonna explain,
oh, a few little things.

14:58.480 --> 15:01.150
Like why he just disappeared
for over a fucking year

15:01.233 --> 15:03.527
without explaining shit
to his best fucking friend.

15:04.278 --> 15:05.404
D, I'm sorry.

15:06.864 --> 15:08.532
He's very sorry.

15:08.616 --> 15:12.411
Yeah, sure. You know what?
I don't know why I'm complaining to you.

15:12.995 --> 15:14.580
Not like he can hear me, right?

15:15.789 --> 15:16.624
Come on.

15:16.707 --> 15:18.250
["Painting Greys" playing]

15:19.835 --> 15:21.462
♪ And I know ♪

15:25.591 --> 15:28.636
♪ Times like these
You just take it slow ♪

15:31.847 --> 15:33.891
♪ Mmm ♪

15:34.308 --> 15:36.018
♪ And there she goes ♪

15:40.105 --> 15:42.816
♪ Heart that pounds like a stereo ♪

15:45.527 --> 15:46.779
Oh, my God.

15:46.862 --> 15:50.157
♪ You take me round and round
Like the merry-go ♪

15:50.240 --> 15:51.283
Really?

15:54.244 --> 15:57.581
♪ But one more ride, baby, here we go ♪

16:01.543 --> 16:02.878
Makes sense.

16:07.341 --> 16:08.467
What does?

16:09.218 --> 16:10.302
Coming here.

16:11.428 --> 16:12.930
You know Superdawg?

16:13.639 --> 16:15.766
Whenever he gets nervous, he needs to eat.

16:16.558 --> 16:19.520
I gotta get something to eat.
You want anything?

16:19.603 --> 16:20.479
I'm okay.

16:20.562 --> 16:21.897
I really miss the malts.

16:22.648 --> 16:25.359
