20:43.242 --> 20:46.411
Okay. All right, that's fine.
Will you just answer me one question?

20:47.246 --> 20:48.413
What?

20:49.498 --> 20:51.416
How many times did the Feds
or Homeland Security

20:51.500 --> 20:52.793
call you in for questioning?

20:54.461 --> 20:56.046
